Miss World 2008, mbipụta nke 58 nke asọmupi Miss World, emere na 13 Disemba n'afo 2008 na Sandton Convention Centre na Johannesburg, South Africa. Na mbụ, asọmupi ahụ ga-ewere ọnọdụ na Kyiv, Ukraine, mana n'ihi nsogbu ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Russo-Georgian na-aga n'ihu n'afọ 2008 na South Ossetia, Miss World Organization kpebiri ịkwapụ asọmpi ahụ n'Ebe Ọwụwa Anyanwụ Europe
Ndị asọmupi 109 si n'akụkụ ụwa niile na-asọmupi maka okpueze ahụ, nke abụọ kachasị elu na afọ 59 nke asọmpi ahụ
Zhang Zilin nke China kpuchiri Ksenia Sukhinova nke Russia dị ka Miss World ọhụrụ.
